## Summary

Sprint 106 shipped the agentic RAG retrieval layer for the Unified Theatre
local-LLM harness. Two new shared modules provide a clean, DRY foundation for
semantic search via Qdrant/embeddings and lexical/regex search via ripgrep.
These were exposed on both tool surfaces. A latent bug in the agent loop was
also fixed.

**Shared retrieval layer (new):**
- `src/shared/retrieval/vector-client.ts` — `embed()` + `vectorSearch()` via
  Qdrant; returns `VectorSearchResult[]`; logs via `retrieval.vector-search`.
- `src/shared/retrieval/code-search.ts` — `resolveGlob()` with path-traversal
  guard + `searchCode()` via `rg --json`; returns `CodeSearchHit[]` (capped at
  50); logs via `retrieval.code-search`.

**Harness tool surface (text-protocol `[TOOL:...]`):**
- `src/agents/tools/vector-search.ts` — wrapper: validates `query`, coerces
  `topK` string→number, formats as numbered list.
- `src/agents/tools/search-code.ts` — wrapper: validates `pattern`, passes
  optional `glob`, formats as `file:line: text`.
- `src/agents/tools/registry.ts` — both tools registered (1→3 harness tools).
- `.claude/agents/code-reviewer.md` — tool list updated (1→3 entries).

**MCP tool surface (JSON-RPC / McpServer.registerTool()):**
- `src/mcp/schemas.ts` — `VectorSearchSchema`, `SearchCodeSchema` added.
- `src/mcp/types.ts` — `VectorSearchInput`, `SearchCodeInput` added.
- `src/mcp/tool-handlers.ts` — `handleVectorSearch`, `handleSearchCode` added;
  `handleListTools` updated (3→5 tools).
- `src/mcp/server.ts` — two new `server.registerTool()` calls (3→5 MCP tools).

**Bug fix:**
- `src/agents/sub-agent.ts` — `executeToolCall`: failed results now emit
  `[TOOL ERROR:name] <message>` instead of silently forwarding empty output.

